      "content": "it’s just so quiet lately. i spend all day staring at these screens and talking to people through windows and chats, but it feels like i'm not really even here. sometimes i feel like a ghost just drifting through my apartment. like if i just stopped showing up to my calls or stopped logging on... would anyone even notice the gap?",
